  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>ivai iraṇṭu cūttiramum uraiyiyaipu nōkki yuṭaṉeḻutappaṭṭatu.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēl, icainiṟai, acainilai, poruḷoṭu puṇartal eṉṟavai mūṉṟeṉpa orucol aṭukku; eṉpuḻi mūṉṟu vakaiyāṉ aṭukkivarappeṟum eṉṟavai ellaiyiṉmaiyāṉ, avai yittuṇai yeṉṉum varaiyaṟai kūṟiṉār īṇṭu eṉpatu.</p>
<p>urai : am mūṉṟaṉuḷ icainiṟaittaṟku aṭukkappaṭum poruḷ nāṉku varampākum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>iraṇṭum aṭukkum, mūṉṟum aṭukkum, nāṉkum aṭukkum, nāṉkiṟantu aṭukkā eṉpatu karuttu.</p>
<p>atu,</p>
<p>'pāṭukō pāṭukō pāṭukō pāṭukō'</p>
<p>eṉa varum.</p>
<p>itu, nāṉku aṭukkiṉa vantatu. icainiṟaiyeṉavē, atu ceyyuṭkeṉpatu muṭintatu.</p>
<p>iṉi, am mūṉṟuṭaṉ poruḷoṭu puṇartalai viraicollaṭukku eṉpatu ; atutāṉ mūṉṟu varampu iṟavātu eṉpatu. 'pāmpu, pāmpu, pāmpu' 'tīt tīt tī' eṉa varum ; iraṇṭu mūṉṟiṟavātu.</p>
<p>maṟṟu, acainilai yiṉaittāl aṭukkum eṉpatu eṟṟāṟ peṟutum eṉiṉ, mūṉṟaṭukkum poruḷoṭu puṇartalai muṟkūṟaṟ pālār, eṉṉai, mūṉṟu nāṉku eṉṉum eṇṇumuṟaimai nōkki avvāṟu collātu mayakkaṅ kūṟiyavataṉāṉ, mūṉṟiṉ kīḻkkumutal iraṇṭallatu illaiyeṉṟē ; avviraṇṭeṇṇiṉ nāṉkākappaṭum acainilai eṉpatu koḷka eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'maṟṟō maṟṟō' 'aḵtē aḵtē' eṉa varum.</p>
<p>iraṇṭiṟavātu eṉpataṉai ilēciṉāṟ koṇṭāṟ, iṭaiccollaṭukkātaliṉ eṉpatu. oḻinta, nālvakaic collum aṭukkum.	(27 - 28)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

